The Oppo Reno 11 5G is a great smartphone and its a worth my money. I think I am sorted for 3-4 years with this great purchase.

Here are some of the pros and cons of the Oppo Reno 11 5G:

Pros:
Premium Curved smooth touch display
Sleek and stylish look
AMOLED display
Fast processor
Good battery backup
wow potraiot mode and telephoto camera
Fast 5G connectivity
Indisplay finger print is quick

Cons:

Lot of adjustment for perfect camera photography
Some minor heating issues when gaming and whatsapp chating together
too many Pre-installed apps, some might find it good too

Overall, the Oppo Reno 11 5G is a great mid-range smartphone that offers a lot of worth. If you're looking for a reliable and affordable 5G phone for long term, then the Oppo Reno 11 5G is a great option.
